(67, 'Soy la Maldad', 'R. L. Stine', 'Montena', '9788484410980', '2001-12', 'Maggie and her friends came to the fortune-teller\'s tent for fun. The old woman who reads her palm will soon have Maggie screaming in horror.', 'Terror, Misterio y Suspenso', 1, 1, 'not_found.jpg'),
