(137, 'El secreto del tanque de aqua', 'María Inés Falconi', 'Editorial desconocida', '9789870413905', '2010', 'While visiting their grandmother one day, Lucas y Rocío are transported back to 1810 at the beginning of Argentina\'s fight for independence.', 'Ficción Niños', 1, 1, 'not_found.jpg'),
